A popular Nigerian politician and former APC youth leader Aspirant, Dada Olusegun has taken to his official Twitter page and reacted after Soludo offered to pay ten million naira reward for information on killers of Anambra Lawmaker.

While reacting to the news on his official Twitter page, Dada Olusegun said; “I remember how they gathered in my @s to abuse me for saying treating Nnamdi Kanu as a celebrity political prisoner will only embolden the terrorists he has unleashed on South East Nigeria. May the Honourable’s soul rest in peace”.
Below is the screen capture of the post;However, this post by Dada Olusegun have generated massive responses from fans and other social media followers. A lot of them reacted by liking the post while others trooped into the comment section to express their reactions from different perspectives.


